在郊區"},{"pid":"6e970db41d2920c203ce0c290fd3c4792a10f07d","tid":663461,"uid":31841,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T10:43:59.000Z","msg":"就咁google search到段咁既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本报广州12月10日电 邵宏军、特约记者杨亚斌报道：今天18时05分，39名新兵从广州乘坐G1076次高速列车经过3个半小时，准点抵达武汉南站。<br />\n<br />\n今冬新兵铁路输送工作开始后，广铁军代处利用武广高铁输送新兵，他们认真拟制计划上报军区和铁路部门，在广州南站开设快速通道，确保高铁输送新兵安全圆满。"},{"pid":"4cbf169e1ac2685e014088738b4c58fa00b8f874","tid":663461,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T02:25:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"992699a751157d52b4833304b97cc3c3c85b6805","tid":663461,"uid":77143,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T02:28:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明係地理問題屈唔到入去，講咁多廢話"},{"pid":"a491384a3b04d38cc679264c7e2ab249fde9c72c","tid":663461,"uid":77143,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T02:30:58.000Z","msg":"你呢個垃圾問題就好似話香港高鐵站點解起係西九而唔係紅磡一樣咁無聊"},{"pid":"c138f5b755ed892cbb3132425b8e9660528929c0","tid":663461,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T02:41:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc58901f0ee3671bbd253b594e80262b44ded2fc","tid":663461,"uid":9685,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T03:05:59.000Z","msg":"係香港用高鐵幫廣州南發展"},{"pid":"6dd8be0e00fc4d1478917b928312b881ed3270ac","tid":663461,"uid":35870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a491384a3b04d38cc679264c7e2ab249fde9c72c","tid":663461,"uid":77143,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T02:30:58.000Z","msg":"你呢個垃圾問題就好似話香港高鐵站點解起係西九而唔係紅磡一樣咁無聊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T13:37:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> really?"}]}